script.name: plugin.complexplan.menu
script.sourceplaintext:
$page.id = 6020 $text.none = read text: page=35 id=676 $text.none = sprintf: fmt='-- %s --', $text.none, null, null, null, null
gosub sub.GetVars
if $a.state == [MEvent.Start] @ START [NULL] -> call script lib.complexplan.getstations : Race=null Search Filter=null Product=null Allow Unknown=[FALSE] Allow Cant Buy=[FALSE]
$tls = get ship array: of race Player class/type=TL $i = size of array $tls while $i dec $i = $tl = $tls[$i] do if $tl -> get amount of ware Build Command Software MK2 in cargo bay set global variable: name='complex.planner.mk2' value=[TRUE] do if $tl -> get amount of ware Build Command Software MK3 in cargo bay set global variable: name='complex.planner.mk3' value=[TRUE] end
if $a.value == 'build.complex' set global variable: name='complex.planner.new' value=[TRUE] $text = read text: page=$page.id id=2012 $input = create input: id='sector.pos', user input=Var/Sector Position, refobj=$a.obj, description=$text, without sector=[FALSE], filterclass=null, racemask=null, flags=null, default=null return $input else gosub sub.StartMenu return $input end
else if $a.state == [MEvent.IsDisabled] $stored.data = get global variable: name='complex.planner.stored' $playing.time = playing time if ! $stored.data $stored.data = array alloc: size=2 $time = 0 set global variable: name='complex.planner.stored' value=$stored.data else $time = $stored.data[0] end
if ! $time OR $playing.time > ( $time + 5 ) $stored.data[0] = $playing.time @ $array = $a.obj -> call script lib.complexplan.getkits : Include HQ=[TRUE] Closest=$a.obj $complex.hub = $array[0] if $complex.hub $stored.data[1] = [FALSE] else $stored.data[1] = [TRUE] end end $ret = $stored.data[1] return $ret
else if $a.state == 'build.tl' @ $ret = [THIS] -> call script plugin.complexplan.deployment : Object=$a.obj State=$a.state Value=$a.value return $ret
else if $a.state == 'save' $text = read text: page=$page.id id=2033 $input = create input: id='save.name', user input=Var/String, refobj=$a.obj, description=$text, without sector=[FALSE], filterclass=null, racemask=null, flags=null, default=$current.complex return $input
else if $a.state == 'sector' OR $a.state == 'sector.pos' if $a.state == 'sector.pos' set global variable: name='complex.planner.pos' value=$a.value $a.value = $a.value[3] end
set global variable: name='complex.planner.sector' value=$a.value set global variable: name='complex.planner.margin' value=0 $tAsteroids = table alloc $tStations = table alloc $tExisting = table alloc $tExternal = table alloc set global variable: name='complex.planner.stations' value=$tStations set global variable: name='complex.planner.asteroids' value=$tAsteroids set global variable: name='complex.planner.existing' value=$tExisting set global variable: name='complex.planner.external' value=$tExternal @ $array = [THIS] -> call script lib.complexplan.getkits : Include HQ=[TRUE] Closest=$a.value set global variable: name='complex.planner.kits' value=$array $upgrades.table = table alloc set global variable: name='complex.planner.upgrades' value=$upgrades.table set global variable: name='complex.planner.adjust' value=null $adjust.station = null gosub sub.CheckAsteroids gosub sub.BuildMenu return $input
else if $a.state == 'startmenu' if $a.value == 'start.new' $text = read text: page=$page.id id=2012 $input = create input: id='sector', user input=Var/Sector, refobj=$a.obj, description=$text, without sector=[FALSE], filterclass=null, racemask=null, flags=null, default=null return $input end
else if $a.state == 'autocomplete' $text = read text: page=$page.id id=317 $input = create input: id='autocomplete.race', user input=Var/Race, refobj=$a.obj, description=$text, without sector=null, filterclass=null, racemask=null, flags=null, default=null return $input
else if $a.state == 'deployment' gosub sub.CheckAsteroids @ $input = [THIS] -> call script plugin.complexplan.deployment : Object=$a.obj State='start' Value=$a.value return $input
else if $a.state == 'asteroid' @ $input = [THIS] -> call script plugin.complexplan.addmine : Object=$a.obj State=$a.state Value=$a.value return $input
else if $a.state == 'product' @ $input = [THIS] -> call script plugin.complexplan.addstation : Object=$a.state State='product' Value=$a.value return $input
else if $a.state == [MEvent.Search] $current.state = $a.value[0] if $current.state == 'addstation' @ $input = [THIS] -> call script plugin.complexplan.addstation : Object=$a.obj State=$a.state Value=$a.value return $input else if $current.state == 'addproduct' @ $input = [THIS] -> call script plugin.complexplan.addproduct : Object=$a.obj State=$a.state Value=$a.value return $input else if $current.state == 'addresource' @ $a.obj = [THIS] -> call script plugin.complexplan.addresource : Object=$a.obj State=$a.state Value=$a.value return $input end
else if $a.state == [MEvent.Finished] gosub sub.ClearVars return null
else if $a.state == [MEvent.Select] $menu.id = $a.value[0] $selection = $a.value[1] if $menu.id == 'menu' if $selection == 'adjusted' $value = $a.value[3] $tStations[$adjust.station] = $value set global variable: name='complex.planner.adjust' value=null $adjust.station = null play sample [Sound.Success] gosub sub.BuildMenu $input = create input return value: update menu=$menu return $input end else if $menu.id == 'deploymenu' if $selection == 'hire.build' gosub sub.CheckAsteroids $ret = create new array, size=6, elements=$sector, $tStations, $tAsteroids, $upgrades.table, $upgrade.level, $tExisting, null, null START [PLAYERSHIP] ->open menu script: script=plugin.complexplan.hireservice, value=$ret else if $selection == 'hire.build.noto' $voice.array = create new array, arguments=[Page.MiscVoice], 135, [Page.MiscVoice], 57, null START speak array: $voice.array prio=60 else if $selection == 'hire.build.cant' $voice.array = create new array, arguments=[Page.MiscVoice], 135, [Page.MiscVoice], 1380, null START speak array: $voice.array prio=60 end end
else if $a.state == [MEvent.Selection] if $adjust.station set global variable: name='complex.planner.adjust' value=null $adjust.station = null gosub sub.BuildMenu return $menu end
else if $a.state == [MEvent.Hotkey] $current.state = $a.value[2] $from = $a.value[0] $value = $a.value[1] if $value == 'info' if is datatype[ $current.state ] == DATATYPE_WARE $input = create input: id='encyclopedia' encyclopedia page, ware=$current.state return $input end end
else if $a.state == [MEvent.Returned] $from = $a.value[0] $current.state = $a.value[1] $value = $a.value[2] if $from == 'encyclopedia' return null end if $from == 'addmine' if not is datatype[ $value ] == DATATYPE_NULL @ $input = [THIS] -> call script plugin.complexplan.addmine : Object=$a.obj State=$a.state Value=$a.value return $input end
else if $from == 'addproduct' if not is datatype[ $value ] == DATATYPE_NULL @ $input = [THIS] -> call script plugin.complexplan.addproduct : Object=$a.obj State=$a.state Value=$a.value return $input end
else if $from == 'addresource' if not is datatype[ $value ] == DATATYPE_NULL @ $input = [THIS] -> call script plugin.complexplan.addresource : Object=$a.obj State=$a.state Value=$a.value return $input end
else if $from == 'startmenu' gosub sub.StartMenu $input = create input return value: update menu=$menu return $menu
else if $from == 'deploymenu' if $current.state == 'build.tl.menu' $input = create menu return to previous menu: value=$value return $input end
else if $from == 'menu' if not is datatype[ $value ] == DATATYPE_NULL if $current.state == 'save.name' gosub sub.GetSavedTable if not $saved.complexes $saved.complexes = table alloc set global variable: name='complex.planner.saved' value=$saved.complexes end set global variable: name='complex.planner.adjust' value=null $adjust.station = null $saved.complexes[$value] = $saved.table else if $current.state == 'build.tl' if $value if $selected.tl -> exists START speak text: page=[Page.MiscVoice] id=131 priority=20 gosub sub.GetSavedTable @ START $selected.tl -> call script !ship.cmd.buildcomplex.std : Plan Data=$saved.table Build Position=$value Restore Previous=[FALSE] Include HQ=[TRUE] end end else if $current.state == 'deploymenu' if $value == 'save' START speak text: page=13 id=131 priority=10 @ = [THIS] -> call script plugin.complexplan.export : Sector=$sector Profit=1 Cycle Time=1 Stations=$tStations asteroids=$tAsteroids Destination='log' else if $value == 'export' START speak text: page=13 id=131 priority=10 @ = [THIS] -> call script plugin.complexplan.export : Sector=$sector Profit=1 Cycle Time=1 Stations=$tStations asteroids=$tAsteroids Destination='export' else if $value == 'build' $ret = create menu return to previous menu: value='build' return $ret else if is datatype[ $value ] == DATATYPE_ARRAY $value = $value[0] if $value if $value -> exists set global variable: name='complex.planner.tl' value=$value $text = read text: page=$page.id id=2012 $input = create input: id='build.tl', user input=Var/Sector Position, refobj=$sector, description=$text, without sector=[TRUE], filterclass=null, racemask=null, flags=null, default=null return $input end end end return null else if $current.state == 'add.existing' if $value -> exists $type = $value -> get ware type code of object $tExisting[$value] = $type remove key $value from table $tExternal gosub sub.BuildMenu return $menu end else if $current.state == 'add.external' if $value -> exists $type = $value -> get ware type code of object $tExternal[$value] = $type remove key $value from table $upgrades.table remove key $value from table $tExisting gosub sub.BuildMenu return $menu end else if $current.state == 'addstation' OR $current.state == 'addproduct' OR $current.state == 'addresource' $val = 1 if is datatype[ $value ] == DATATYPE_ARRAY $val = $value[1] skip if is datatype[ $val ] == DATATYPE_INT $val = 1 $value = $value[0] end $amt = $tStations[$value] skip if $amt $amt = 0 $amt = $amt + $val $tStations[$value] = $amt gosub sub.BuildMenu return $menu else if $current.state == 'autocomplete.race' @ $ret = [THIS] -> call script lib.complexplan.complete : Sector=$sector Station table=$tStations Asteroid table=$tAsteroids Compact?=[TRUE] Favoured Race=$value Allow Unknown=[FALSE] Allow Cant Buy=[TRUE] Existing Stations=$tExisting if $ret $tStations = $ret[0] $tAsteroids = $ret[1] gosub sub.CheckAsteroids set global variable: name='complex.planner.stations' value=$tStations set global variable: name='complex.planner.asteroids' value=$tAsteroids gosub sub.BuildMenu return $menu end else if $current.state == 'removestation' $val = 1 if is datatype[ $value ] == DATATYPE_ARRAY $val = $value[1] $value = $value[0] end
if is datatype[ $value ] == DATATYPE_OBJECT remove key $value from table $tAsteroids else $amt = $tStations[$value] $amt = $amt - $val if $amt > 0 $tStations[$value] = $amt else remove key $value from table $tStations end end gosub sub.BuildMenu return $menu else if $current.state == 'addproduct' OR $current.state == 'addresource' if is datatype[ $value ] == DATATYPE_ARRAY $value = $value[0] end gosub sub.BuildMenu return $input else if $current.state == 'addmine' $value.asterod = $value[1] $value.station = $value[0][0] $tAsteroids[$value.asterod] = $value.station gosub sub.BuildMenu return $menu end end end
else if $a.state == [MEvent.TradeBar] $current.state = $a.value[0] if $current.state == 'addstation' @ $input = [THIS] -> call script plugin.complexplan.addstation : Object=$a.obj State=$a.state Value=$a.value return $input end
else if $a.state == [MEvent.Switch] $current.state = $a.value[0] if $current.state == 'menu' $switch.type = $a.value[1] $value = $a.value[2] if $switch.type == 'margin' set global variable: name='complex.planner.margin' value=$value else if $switch.type == 'upgrade.level' set global variable: name='complex.planner.upgrade' value=$value end gosub sub.BuildMenu return $menu else if $current.state == 'addstation' @ $input = [THIS] -> call script plugin.complexplan.addstation : Object=$a.obj State=$a.state Value=$a.value return $input else if $current.state == 'addproduct' @ $input = [THIS] -> call script plugin.complexplan.addproduct : Object=$a.obj State=$a.state Value=$a.value return $input end
else if $a.state == 'add' @ $input = [THIS] -> call script plugin.complexplan.addstation : Object=$a.obj State='start' Value=null return $input
else if $a.state == 'remove' @ $input = [THIS] -> call script plugin.complexplan.removestation : Object=$a.obj State='start' Value=null return $input
else if $a.state == 'add.mine' @ $input = [THIS] -> call script plugin.complexplan.addmine : Object=$a.obj State='start' Value=null return $input
else if $a.state == 'add.resource' @ $input = [THIS] -> call script plugin.complexplan.addresource : Object=$a.obj State='start' Value=$a.value return $input
else if $a.state == 'add.product' @ $input = [THIS] -> call script plugin.complexplan.addproduct : Object=$a.obj State='start' Value=null return $input
else if $a.state == 'add.existing' $filter = create new array, arguments=Factory, null, null, null, null $read.text = read text: page=$page.id id=2159 $input = create input: id='add.existing', user input=Var/Station owned by Player, refobj=$sector, description=$read.text, without sector=[TRUE], filterclass=$filter, racemask=null, flags=null, default=null return $input
else if $a.state == 'add.external' $filter = create new array, arguments=Factory, null, null, null, null $read.text = read text: page=$page.id id=2162 $input = create input: id=$a.state, user input=Var/Station owned by Player, refobj=$sector, description=$read.text, without sector=[FALSE], filterclass=$filter, racemask=null, flags=null, default=null return $input
else if $a.state == [MEvent.Escape] if $adjust.station $adjust.station = null set global variable: name='complex.planner.adjust' value=null gosub sub.BuildMenu return $menu end
else if $a.state == [MEvent.Context] $from = $a.value[0] $current.state = $a.value[1] $value = $a.value[2] if $from == 'startmenu' if $value == 'open' $sector = $saved.complexes[$current.state]['sector'] set global variable: name='complex.planner.sector' value=$sector $i = $saved.complexes[$current.state]['margin'] set global variable: name='complex.planner.margin' value=$i $i = $saved.complexes[$current.state]['stations'] $i = clone table $i set global variable: name='complex.planner.stations' value=$i $i = $saved.complexes[$current.state]['asteroids'] $i = clone table $i set global variable: name='complex.planner.asteroids' value=$i $i = $saved.complexes[$current.state]['existing'] $i = clone table $i set global variable: name='complex.planner.existing' value=$i $i = $saved.complexes[$current.state]['external'] if $i $i = clone table $i else $i = table alloc end set global variable: name='complex.planner.external' value=$i $i = $saved.complexes[$current.state]['upgrade'] set global variable: name='complex.planner.upgrade' value=$i $i = $saved.complexes[$current.state]['levels'] $i = clone table $i set global variable: name='complex.planner.upgrades' value=$i set global variable: name='complex.planner.current' value=$current.state gosub sub.GetVars @ $array = [THIS] -> call script lib.complexplan.getkits : Include HQ=[TRUE] Closest=$sector set global variable: name='complex.planner.kits' value=$array gosub sub.BuildMenu return $input else if $value == 'delete' remove key $current.state from table $saved.complexes gosub sub.StartMenu $input = create input return value: update menu=$menu return $input end else if $from == 'menu' if $value == 'info' if is datatype[ $current.state ] == DATATYPE_STRING $obj = convert serialised string to object: string=$current.state if $obj -> exists $input = create input: id='info' object info page, object=$obj return $input end else $input = create input: id='info' encyclopedia page, ware=$current.state return $input end else if $value == 'remove' if is datatype[ $current.state ] == DATATYPE_STRING $obj = convert serialised string to object: string=$current.state if $obj -> exists remove key $obj from table $upgrades.table remove key $obj from table $tExisting remove key $obj from table $tExternal gosub sub.BuildMenu $input = create input return value: update menu=$menu return $input end end else if $value == 'info.ast' $asteroid = convert serialised string to object: string=$current.state $current.state = $tAsteroids[$asteroid] $input = create input: id='info' encyclopedia page, ware=$current.state return $input else if $value == 'xl' OR $value == 'xxl' OR $value == 'm' OR $value == 'l' OR $value == 'scale.none' if is datatype[ $current.state ] == DATATYPE_STRING $asteroid = convert serialised string to object: string=$current.state if $asteroid -> exists $current.state = $asteroid end end $upgrades.table[$current.state] = $value gosub sub.BuildMenu $input = create input return value: update menu=$menu return $input else if $value == 'default.scale' if is datatype[ $current.state ] == DATATYPE_STRING $asteroid = convert serialised string to object: string=$current.state if $asteroid -> exists $current.state = $asteroid end end remove key $current.state from table $upgrades.table gosub sub.BuildMenu $input = create input return value: update menu=$menu return $input else if $value == 'default.scale.ast' $asteroid = convert serialised string to object: string=$current.state remove key $asteroid from table $upgrades.table gosub sub.BuildMenu $input = create input return value: update menu=$menu return $input else if $value == 'remove.station' remove key $current.state from table $tStations gosub sub.BuildMenu $input = create input return value: update menu=$menu return $input else if $value == 'remove.ast' $asteroid = convert serialised string to object: string=$current.state remove key $asteroid from table $tAsteroids gosub sub.BuildMenu $input = create input return value: update menu=$menu return $input else if $value == 'adjust.qty' set global variable: name='complex.planner.adjust' value=$current.state $adjust.station = $current.state gosub sub.BuildMenu $input = create input return value: update menu=$menu return $input end end
else if $a.state == 'menu' if is datatype[ $a.value ] == DATATYPE_ARRAY $a.value = $a.value[0] end if $a.value == 'build' return [TRUE] end
else if $a.state == [MEvent.Cancelled] if $is.new.complex if $a.value == 'menu' $text = read text: page=$page.id id=2012 $input = create input: id='sector.pos', user input=Var/Sector Position, refobj=$a.obj, description=$text, without sector=[FALSE], filterclass=null, racemask=null, flags=null, default=null return $input end else if $a.value == 'menu' OR $a.value == 'sector' gosub sub.StartMenu return $input end end
else if $a.state == [MEvent.Arguments] if $is.new.complex gosub sub.GetSavedTable $sector.ps = get global variable: name='complex.planner.pos' $ret = create new array, arguments=$sector.ps, $saved.table, null, null, null return $ret end
else if $a.state == [MEvent.Finished] gosub sub.ClearVars return null end
return null
* =====================================
sub.GetSavedTable: $saved.table = table alloc $saved.table['sector'] = $sector $cloned = clone table $tStations $saved.table['stations'] = $cloned $cloned = clone table $tAsteroids $saved.table['asteroids'] = $cloned $cloned = clone table $tExisting $saved.table['existing'] = $cloned if $tExternal $cloned = clone table $tExternal $saved.table['external'] = $cloned end $saved.table['margin'] = $margin $saved.table['upgrade'] = $upgrade.level $cloned = clone table $upgrades.table $saved.table['levels'] = $cloned endsub
sub.StartMenu: $menu = create custom menu array $text = read text: page=$page.id id=2031 $text = sprintf: fmt='[%s]', $text, null, null, null, null add custom menu item to array $menu: text=$text returnvalue='start.new' if $saved.complexes if size of table $saved.complexes add section to custom menu: $menu $array = get keys: table=$saved.complexes $array = sort array $array $array = reverse array $array $i = size of array $array while $i dec $i = $name = $array[$i] $context = create context menu $text = read text: page=$page.id id=2034 add context menu entry: menu=$context, text=$text, icon=113, returnvalue='open', hotkey=null, disabled=[FALSE] $text = read text: page=1904 id=120210 add context menu entry: menu=$context, text=$text, icon=66, returnvalue='delete', hotkey=null, disabled=[FALSE] $ret = create menu return value: context menu, id=$name, menu=$context, dynamic=[FALSE] $text = $saved.complexes[$name]['sector'] $text = create text for custom menu, left=$name, right=$text add custom menu item to array $menu: text=$text returnvalue=$ret end end end
set menu option: $menu, icon=145
$title = read text: page=35 id=1104334 $text = read text: page=$page.id id=2032 $input = create input: id='startmenu' menu=$menu title=$title description=$text callback=0 endsub
sub.DrawExisting: if $indent $text.colour = [MenuColour.Disabled] else $text.colour = [MenuColour.Normal] end $text.columns = array alloc: size=5 $text.col = $station.obj ->create custom menu string object icon $text.col = create custom menu column string, position=$indent length=10 right=[FALSE] colour=$text.colour text=$text.col $text.columns[0] = $text.col $text.col = $station.obj -> get name $upgrade.obj = $station.obj gosub sub.GetScaleFactor gosub sub.ComputeEff $upgrade.obj = null if $upgrades.table[$obj] $upgrade.station = $upgrades.table[$obj] if $upgrade.station == 'scale.none' $read.text = null else $amt = $upgrade.lookup.table[$upgrade.station] $read.text = get scale factor name: scale=$amt end do if $read.text $text.col = sprintf: fmt='%s -> %s', $text.col, $read.text, null, null, null else $amt = $station.obj ->get station scale factor if $scale.factor > $amt gosub sub.GetUpgradeName $text.col = sprintf: fmt='%s -> %s', $text.col, $read.text, null, null, null end end $pos = $indent + 12 $len = 300 - $pos $text.col = create custom menu column string, position=$pos length=$len right=[FALSE] colour=$text.colour text=$text.col $text.columns[1] = $text.col $len = $COL.PRODUCT - $COL.QTY $type = $station.obj -> get ware type code of object if is station type a mine: stationtype=$type $yield = $station.obj ->get production efficiency $text.col = convert number $yield to string else $text.col = '-' end $text.col = create custom menu column string, position=$COL.QTY length=$len right=[TRUE] colour=$text.colour text=$text.col $text.columns[2] = $text.col $len = $COL.TIME - $COL.PRODUCT $product = $station.obj -> get product ware $text.col = sprintf: fmt='%s', $product, null, null, null, null $text.col = create custom menu column string, position=$COL.PRODUCT length=$len right=[TRUE] colour=$text.colour text=$text.col $text.columns[3] = $text.col $len = $COL.PRICE - $COL.TIME @ $ret = [THIS] -> call script lib.complexplan.getproductinfo : Station Type=$type Efficency=$eff IsPlayer=[TRUE] Scale Factor=$scale.factor $time = $ret[0] $text.col = format time: $time $text.col = create custom menu column string, position=$COL.TIME length=$len right=[TRUE] colour=$text.colour text=$text.col $text.columns[4] = $text.col endsub
sub.DrawStations: if $arg.Table if size of table $arg.Table $text.columns = array alloc: size=4 $text.col = create custom menu column string, position=0 length=300 right=[FALSE] colour=null text=$arg.Header $text.columns[0] = $text.col $len = $COL.PRODUCT - $COL.QTY $text.col = read text: page=35 id=717 $text.col = create custom menu column string, position=$COL.QTY length=$len right=[TRUE] colour=null text=$text.col $text.columns[1] = $text.col $len = $COL.TIME - $COL.PRODUCT $text.col = read text: page=35 id=9306 $text.col = create custom menu column string, position=$COL.PRODUCT length=$len right=[TRUE] colour=null text=$text.col $text.columns[2] = $text.col $len = $COL.PRICE - $COL.TIME $text.col = read text: page=35 id=1102506 $text.col = create custom menu column string, position=$COL.TIME length=$len right=[TRUE] colour=null text=$text.col $text.columns[3] = $text.col add custom menu heading to array $menu: title=$text.columns
$sorted.list = sort table keys: table=$arg.Table $size = size of array $sorted.list $i = 0 while $i < $size $obj = $sorted.list[$i] inc $i =
if $obj -> is of class Complex Hub $text.columns = array alloc: size=2 $text.col = $obj ->create custom menu string object icon $text.col = create custom menu column string, position=0 length=10 right=[FALSE] colour=null text=$text.col $text.columns[0] = $text.col $text.col = $obj -> get name $text.col = create custom menu column string, position=12 length=288 right=[FALSE] colour=null text=$text.col $text.columns[1] = $text.col else $station = $obj -> get ware type code of object $station.obj = $obj $indent = 0 gosub sub.DrawExisting end
$serial = $obj -> serialise object $context = create context menu $read.text = read text: page=[Page.Menus] id=812 add context menu entry: menu=$context, text=$read.text, icon=29, returnvalue='info', hotkey=[Key.Identity], disabled=[FALSE] $read.text = read text: page=[Page.Menus] id=1107 add context menu entry: menu=$context, text=$read.text, icon=66, returnvalue='remove', hotkey=null, disabled=[FALSE] if $arg.Upgrade add context menu separator: menu=$context $read.text = read text: page=6020 id=2037 add context sub menu entry: menu=$context, text=$read.text, icon=118, disabled=[FALSE] if $upgrades.table[$obj] $scale = $upgrades.table[$obj] if $scale == 'scale.none' $current.info.text = read text: page=[Page.Menus] id=676 else $scale = $upgrade.lookup.table[$scale] $current.info.text = get scale factor name: scale=$scale end else $current.info.text = read text: page=6020 id=2027 end add context menu info line: menu=$context, name=$read.text, value=$current.info.text $read.text = read text: page=6020 id=2027 add context menu entry: menu=$context, text=$read.text, icon=118, returnvalue='default.scale', hotkey=null, disabled=[FALSE]
